<template>
  <IonCard @click="$emit('wow!!!!!', id)">
    <IonCardHeader>
      <IonCardTitle>{{ name }}</IonCardTitle>
      <IonCardContent>{{ topic }}</IonCardContent>
      <p/>
      <IonIcon :icon="planet" />
    </IonCardHeader>
  </IonCard>
</template>

<script>
import {
  IonCard,
  IonCardHeader,
  IonCardSubtitle,
  IonCardTitle,
  IonIcon,
} from '@ionic/vue';
import { planet } from 'ionicons/icons';

export default {
  name: "GroupItem",
  setup() {
    return {
      planet,
    }
  },
  components: { IonIcon, IonCard, IonCardHeader, IonCardTitle,},
  props: {
    name: String,
    id: String,
    topic: String,
  }
}

</script>

<style scoped>
</style>
